    • methodPermitted

      protected boolean methodPermitted​(org.consensusj.jsonrpc.JsonRpcRequest request)
      Check that the JSON-RPC method is permitted. This means it is on the allow list (if an allow list is present) and not on the deny list.
      Parameters:
      request - The incoming request
      Returns:
      true if permitted, false if denied
